Subject: E Discovery will not generated the reports
Description: After applying the scanning the reports are not generated multiple devices
What_We_Know__c:
The partitions from Ediscovery are time labeled. For example the partition with time label June last year should be selected for the search.

Keep in mind that when a new scan is started all previous scan results are lost. An Audit Log backup for eDiscovery is recommended before starting a new scan. A message with this recommendation is displayed in a popup when starting a new scan.
Next_Steps__c: Inform the customer about how partition are working!
